args: What the hell are those damn smiths\nplaying at holding the Golden Anvil\nin a place like this?
No ideaâ€”and I don't care, neither.\nAin't like a bunch of metalheads\ncan stand against the Empire!
Haw haw haw! So true!\n...Wait, here they come.
They've lined all their weapons up on\na rack like it's some kind of show.
Ha! What fools! Time to go catch us\na gaggle of blacksmiths.
Heh. Like lambs to the slaughter...\nStonetech engine, activate!
Heh. Any rokkan can design a mechanism\nto send a few weapons through the air.
Now that our enemy is faltering,\nthis is our chance! Push them back!
Leave it to us. Let's go, sisters!
I'm gonna show those Empire dogs\njust how sharp my weapons are!
Ha! I'll kill ten times your number!
We'll protect the Golden Anvil\nwith our own weapons!
C-clearly we were wrong to\nunderestimate these blacksmiths.
I was hoping to take them back uninjured,\nbut I have no choice. ...BRING IT OUT!
Do we have to fight THAT?!
This may be a little above your pay grade\nas smiths, guys. Leave the fiend to us!
I'll drench this thing to the bone!\nTake this! Droplet Slash!
Hee hee! Now I've got you!
And for the finishing blow...\nArise, O flame! Haaaah!
Now THAT'S teamwork! No ugly fiend\ncould possibly stand againstâ€”
Ha ha! This fiend's outer skin is tougher\nthan the continent's hardest ore!\nNo blade can pierce it!
Guess that means it's up to me.
Activating stonetech engine!\nReactor mana charge risin'...\n50 percent... 80 percent...100 percent!
Glory be! She reduced the skin\nof that thing to ash!
Haw haw haw! Look at 'em run!
Oh man. We woulda been three dead\nducks without Lazry and her arm.
Nay, the day wasn't won by meâ€”\nit was won by all of us. After all,\nmany hands make light work.
Are you gonna join our workshop now?
N-nay! I can't compete against ye\nif I'm part of your team!
Heh. Only joking, Lazry. Don't worry.
But we DO want you to help in\nour fight against the Empire.
Your fight? ...Aye, of course. That explains\nwhy you've such skill at battlin' fiends.
The Empire won't stop comin' after\nsmiths and engineers and the like.
But when they do, I'll be there\nto stand against 'em.
Hee hee! They won't know what hit 'em\nwhen you unleash that arm!
Thanks, lasses. But now, there's still\nthe little matter of the Golden Anvil...
Oh, you know we're comin' for you.\nCome on, girls! Let's do this!
This weapon represents all of our\nhard work and bonding as sisters!
Aye, and mine represents the bond\nI share with all rokkans.
I had a certain engineer make me a\nsuper-hot furnace and a special grinder...
And I used 'em to put all that I am into\nthis weapon!
And now, the moment you've been waiting\nfor. The winner of the Golden Anvil is...!
